# Step 11: Email Alerts

Email alerts notify customers when their support case is resolved.

---

# Step 1: Create Email Template

Go to Setup

Search **Email Templates**

Click **New Email Template**

Select **Classic Email Template**

Related Object → **Case**

---

## Template Details

Template Name
Case_Resolution_Email

Subject
Your Case Has Been Resolved – {!Case.CaseNumber}

Email Body

Hello {!Case.Contact},

Your case has been successfully resolved.

Case Number: {!Case.CaseNumber}
Status: {!Case.Status}

If you have further questions, feel free to contact us.

Thank you
Support Team

Click **Save**

---

# Step 2: Create Email Alert

Go to **Setup**

Search **Email Alerts**

Click **New Email Alert**

Configure

Object → Case

Email Template → Case_Resolution_Email

Recipients → Contact Email

Click **Save**

---

# Step 3: Record Triggered Flow

Create **Record Triggered Flow**

Object → Case

Trigger → When Record Updated

Condition

Status = Closed

---

## Add Action

Action Type → Send Email Alert

Email Alert → Case Resolution Email

---

# Step 4: Activate Flow

Save Flow

Flow Name
Case Resolution Email Flow

Click **Activate**

---

# Result

When a case status changes to **Closed**, the system automatically sends a **Case Resolution Email** to the customer.
